{"tid":2088932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部：中共今天風華正茂","createTime":"2020-07-01T12:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T15:36:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"099f7f62f8fc752a65a6b1390ddc21d67fa068dd","tid":2088932,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:08:48.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧近日多次攻擊中國共產黨和中國政治制度，稱要把中國人民的希望和夢想，同中國共產黨的希望和夢想區分開。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人趙立堅表示，今天是中國共產黨成立99周年，首先祝中國共產黨生日快樂，又指中國共產黨的夢想和中國人民的夢想是同一個，就是實現中華民族偉大復興，這個夢想一定能實現。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅稱，今天的中國共產黨恰是風華正茂，今天也恰恰是蓬佩奧之流特別難受的日子。蓬佩奧之流靠撒謊詆毀中國共產黨，割斷中國共產黨同中國人民的血肉聯繫，是在做「白日夢」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2508947/外交部稱中共風華正茂+蓬佩奧之流特別難受\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2508947%2F%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E9%A2%A8%E8%8F%AF%E6%AD%A3%E8%8C%82%2B%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E4%B9%8B%E6%B5%81%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E9%9B%A3%E5%8F%97&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=ec10c332\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2508947/外交部稱中共風華正茂+蓬佩奧之流特別難受</a>"},{"pid":"1a3b9d8d42ae710aad26d9924a3cb2923bb2bbde","tid":2088932,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:10:07.000Z","msg":"今日国慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf6656d95aac73dbd17066df448e7d356c2f69e","tid":2088932,"uid":41343,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:10:41.000Z","msg":"99歲風華正茂？"},{"pid":"5cf1dd6374383cb40d21596be2c5f082c16cc6af","tid":2088932,"uid":345989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1a3b9d8d42ae710aad26d9924a3cb2923bb2bbde","tid":2088932,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:10:07.000Z","msg":"今日国慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:11:07.000Z","msg":"建黨唔